snippet.title: InfestStation - Teaser - Q3 2023 v1.4
snippet.description:
A teaser clip for the upcoming game InfestStation by Atom Switch. All footage is running and captured in real time inside of Unreal Engine 5.

This video represents a game that is currently in development and is not representative of the final product.

https://atomswitch.dev     https://infeststation.com
